```

**BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES Map (라인 48-55)**
```typescript
private readonly BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES = new Map<string, string>([
  ["file_read",     "read_file"],
  ["file_write",    "write_file"],
  ["http_request",  "network"],
  ["http_get",      "network"],
  ["process_spawn", "spawn_process"],
  ["eval",          "execute_code"],
]);
