**checkBuiltinCapability() (라인 85-98)**
```typescript
private checkBuiltinCapability(builtinName: string): void {
  const required = this.BUILTIN_REQUIRED_CAPABILITIES.get(builtinName);
  if (!required) return; // 안전한 builtins (print, len 등) 통과

  const caps = this.getCurrentCapabilities();
  const hasCapability = caps.some(c => c.cap === required);

  if (!hasCapability) {
    this.runtimeError(
      `[CapabilityError] '${builtinName}' requires capability '${required}', ` +
      `but current function does not declare it`
    );
  }
}
```

**getCurrentCapabilities() (라인 100-104)**
```typescript
private getCurrentCapabilities(): Array<{cap: string; arg?: string}> {
  if (this.frames.length === 0) return [];
  return this.frames[this.frames.length - 1].capabilities;
}
```

